
& lastkills
 
 >> Help: Lastkills (Informational Command)
 -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
 Syntax: lastkills
 Syntax: lastkills/mine
 
 The 'lastkills' command in its various various forms gives you information on
 the most recent kills on the Frontier:
 
 - The first form shows the last 15 kills for the entire playerbase, what unit
   the killer was in, and what unit the victim was in.
 - The second form shows only your last 15 kills, what unit you were in, and
   what unit your victim was in.
 
